snippet.title: Early Teaser for the Boomer Shooter Mekkablood
snippet.description:
This is an early teaser of what's to come with the Boomer shooter / Retro FPS Mekkablood. Specifically the enemy ai, and updates to the movement system. Set to release in 2024. 


KRUMB Games discord server! https://discord.gg/u8wF5J92Y2
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/KRUMBGames

Music by Suno https://www.suno.ai/
